%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdiwali-2024-know-all-about-muhurat-trading-6909560%5C%22%3EMuhurat%20trading%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20it%20is%20called%2C%20is%20an%20annual%20ritual%20in%20the%20Indian%20share%20market%20that%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Hindu%20calendar%20known%20as%20Samvat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikram%20Samvat%20is%20a%20lunisolar%20calendar%20that%20runs%2057%20years%20ahead%20of%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar.%20This%20Diwali%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20Samvat%202081.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuhurat%20trading%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Hindu%20tradition%2C%20the%20word%20'Muhurat'%20means%20an%20auspicious%20time.%20Muhurat%20trading%20is%20a%20ritual%20followed%20by%20Indian%20stock%20traders%20that%20is%20considered%20auspicious%20for%20investing%20in%20shares.%20It%20is%20unique%20only%20to%20the%20Indian%20share%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20hour-long%20muhurat%20trading%20session%20will%20begin%20at%206%20pm%20today%20on%20both%20the%20National%20Stock%20Exchange%20and%20the%20Bombay%20Stock%20Exchange.%20The%20pre-opening%20session%20will%20be%20from%205%3A45%20pm-6%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20market%2C%20however%2C%20will%20be%20closed%20during%20its%20usual%20hours%20on%20Friday%3A%209%3A15%20am-3%3A30%20pm.%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20are%20market%20holidays%2C%20as%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20muhurat%20trading%20session%20is%20considered%20auspicious%20for%20long-term%20investors%20planning%20to%20begin%20their%20financial%20journey.%20One%20may%20consider%20large-cap%20stocks%20for%20such%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20bullish%20due%20to%20the%20festive%20spirit%20despite%20being%20in%20the%20red%20for%20most%20of%20October.%20Sensex%2C%20which%20is%20an%20indicator%20for%20the%20top%2030%20BSE%20stocks%2C%20ended%20below%2080%2C000%20points%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20session%20last%20afternoon%20after%20crashing%20from%20its%20peak%20of%2085%2C000-plus%20over%20a%20month%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStocks%20to%20watch%20out%20for%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMCX%20is%20among%20the%20stocks%20to%20watch%20out%20for%20today%20after%20Praveena%20Rai%20took%20charge%20as%20its%20MD%20and%20CEO%20on%20Thursday.%20Reliance%20is%20also%20in%20the%20spotlight%20after%20the%20European%20Union%20approved%20its%20joint%20venture%20with%20Walt%20Disney%20Co.%20for%20Jio%20for%20its%20entertainment%20business.%20Bonus%20shares%20issued%20by%20the%20company%20are%20also%20set%20to%20start%20trading%20on%20bourses%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarayana%20Hrudayalaya%20and%20Tata%20Investment%20Corp%2C%20which%20released%20their%20second-quarter%20earnings%20after%20Thursday%20market%20hours%2C%20may%20also%20impact%20market%20sentiment.%20The%20market%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20react%20to%20Bonanda%20Engineering's%20earnings%20for%20the%20September%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730437200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fl8lra8j_bse-generic-share-market-generic-sensex-generic-pti_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fmuhurat-trading-2024-indian-share-market-opens-in-evening-only-once-a-year-heres-why-6919335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20share%20market%20will%20open%20for%20an%20hour%20this%20evening%20for%20a%20special%20trading%20session%20on%20Diwali.%20Muhurat%20trading%20session%2C%20as%20it%20is%20called%2C%20is%20an%20annual%20ritual%20in%20the%20Indian%20share%20market%20that%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Hindu%20calendar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fmuhurat-trading-2024-indian-share-market-opens-in-evening-only-once-a-year-heres-why-6919335%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Office%20of%20Shei