%2C%20minister%20in%20charge%20of%20cooperation%20with%20Spain's%20regions%2C%20told%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year's%20worth%20of%20rain%20fell%20in%20eight%20hours%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20Valencia%20region%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragedy%20is%20already%20Spain's%20worst%20flood-related%20disaster%20in%20modern%20history%2C%20and%20meteorologists%20say%20human-driven%20climate%20change%20is%20making%20such%20extreme%20weather%20events%20more%20frequent%20and%20destructive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20at%20least%20185%20people%20died%20in%20heavy%20flooding%20in%20Germany.%20Prior%20to%20that%2C%20209%20people%20died%20in%20Romania%20in%201970%20and%20floods%20in%20Portugal%20in%201967%20killed%20nearly%20500%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20teams%20on%20Thursday%20discovered%20the%20bodies%20of%20eight%20people%2C%20including%20a%20local%20policeman%2C%20who%20had%20been%20trapped%20in%20a%20garage%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Valencia%2C%20Mayor%20Maria%20Jose%20Catala%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20neighbourhood%20of%20La%20Torre%2C%20she%20said%2C%20a%2045-year-old%20woman%20was%20also%20found%20dead%20in%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20people%20carrying%20bags%20or%20pushing%20shopping%20trolleys%20could%20be%20seen%20on%20Thursday%20crossing%20a%20pedestrian%20bridge%20over%20the%20Turia%20River%20from%20La%20Torre%20into%20Valencia%20city%20centre%20to%20stock%20up%20on%20essential%20supplies%20such%20as%20toilet%20paper%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20politicians%20accused%20the%20central%20government%20in%20Madrid%20of%20acting%20too%20slowly%20to%20warn%20residents%20and%20send%20in%20rescue%20teams%2C%20prompting%20the%20Interior%20Ministry%20to%20say%20regional%20authorities%20were%20responsible%20for%20civil%20protection%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20people%20wouldn't%20have%20died%20if%20they%20had%20been%20warned%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Villaescusa%2C%20a%20neighbour%20and%20manager%20of%20a%20local%20supermarket%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaribel%20Albalat%2C%20mayor%20of%20the%20nearby%20town%20of%20Paiporta%2C%20said%20residents%20were%20not%20warned%20of%20the%20imminent%20danger%20of%20flooding.%20She%20said%2062%20people%20had%20died%20in%20her%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20elderly%20people%20inside%20their%20homes%20and%20people%20who%20went%20to%20get%20their%20cars.%20It%20was%20a%20trap%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20TVE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECLINGING%20TO%20PILLAR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Godelleta%2C%20a%20town%2037%20km%20(23%20miles)%20west%20of%20Valencia%20city%2C%20Antonio%20Molina%2C%2052%2C%20described%20how%20he%20survived%20by%20clinging%20to%20a%20pillar%20on%20a%20neighbour's%20porch%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20water%20reached%20his%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMolina's%20home%20suffered%20two%20major%20floods%20in%202018%20and%202020%20and%20he%20blamed%20authorities%20for%20allowing%20construction%20of%20residential%20buildings%20in%20depressions%20where%20water%20accumulates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20to%20live%20here%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20tearfully.%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20we%20get%20a%20couple%20of%20raindrops%2C%20we're%20already%20checking%20our%20phones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20floods%20have%20battered%20Valencia's%20infrastructure%2C%20sweeping%20away%20bridges%2C%20roads%20and%20rail%20tracks%2C%20and%20submerged%20farmland%20in%20a%20region%20that%20produces%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20Spain's%20citrus%20crops%20like%20oranges%2C%20which%20the%20country%20exports%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2080%20km%20(50%20miles)%20of%20roads%20in%20the%20eastern%20region%20were%20seriously%20damaged%20or%20impassable%2C%20said%20Transport%20Minister%20Oscar%20Puente.%20Many%20were%20blocked%20by%20abandoned%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%20there%20are%20dead%20bodies%20in%20some%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20Puente%20told%20reporters%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20would%20take%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%20to%20re-establish%20the%20high-speed%20train%20connection%20between%20Valencia%20and%20Madrid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisiting%20a%20rescue%20coordination%20centre%20near%20Valencia%20city%2C%20Spanish%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20urged%20people%20to%20stay%20at%20home%20due%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20more%20stormy%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20to%20safeguard%20as%20many%20lives%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hard-hit%20rural%20town%20of%20Utiel%2C%20some%2085%20km%20(53%20miles)%20inland%2C%20the%20Magro%20River%20burst%20its%20banks%2C%20sending%20up%20to%20three%20metres%20(9.8%20feet)%20of%20water%20into%20the%20mostly%20single-storey%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUtiel's%20mayor%2C%20Ricardo%20Gabaldon%2C%20said%20at%20least%20six%20people%20died%20in%20the%20town%20of%20about%2012%2C000%2C%20most%20of%20them%20elderly%20or%20disabled%20people%20who%20were%20unable%20to%20clamber%20to%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20used%20water%20pumps%20carried%20on%20tractors%20as%20they%20started%20to%20clean%20up%20on%20Thursday%2C%20with%20children%20helping%20to%20sweep%20the%20sidewalks.%20Ruined%20household%20appliances%20and%20furniture%20were%20piled%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20roads%20and%20elderly%20people%20struggled%20to%20walk%20in%20the%20slippery%2C%20mud-coated%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPope%20Francis%20said%20he%20was%20praying%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20region.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20close%20to%20them%20in%20this%20moment%20of%20catastrophe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20group%20Climate%20Central%20said%20in%20a%20report%20on%20Th