The%20Diplomat.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22584fa967-ca6b-4e23-a516-7caf1ab356f2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20major%20death%20in%20the%20season%20finale%20throws%20Grace%20and%20Kate%20into%20chaos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKate%20learns%20that%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20attack%2C%20which%20was%20executed%20by%20a%20Russian%20mercenary%2C%20was%20a%20false%20flag.%20Right-wing%20figure%20Margaret%20Roylin%20confesses%20to%20Tory%20Prime%20Minister%20Nicolas%20Trowbridge%2C%20whom%20she%20previously%20advised%2C%20that%20she%20orchestrated%20the%20entire%20incident%20to%20help%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20rally%20behind%20Trowbridge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20specifically%2C%20to%20prevent%20Scottish%20succession.%20The%20attack%2C%20however%2C%20was%20much%20more%20severe%20than%20intended%2C%20killing%20British%20sailors%20in%20the%20process%2C%20and%20Trowbridge%20reacts%20with%20abject%20fury%20and%20attempts%20to%20choke%20Roylin%20with%20his%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Kate%20warms%20to%20Grace%20Penn%2C%20the%20vice%20president%2C%20after%20she%20arrives%20in%20London.%20After%20seeing%20Grace%20interact%20with%20Trowbridge%2C%20Kate%20decides%20to%20stop%20pursuing%20the%20vice%20presidency%2C%20and%20moves%20to%20recommend%20that%20Grace%20stay%20in%20office.%20Her%20husband%20Hal%20stops%20her%20from%20doing%20so%2C%20and%20delivers%20a%20devastating%20bit%20of%20information%3A%20Roylin%20didn't%20mastermind%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20%E2%80%94%20Grace%20Penn%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20season%20finale%2C%20Kate%20signals%20to%20Grace%20that%20she's%20aware%20of%20her%20involvement%20in%20the%20incident.%20In%20turn%2C%20Grace%20explains%20that%20she%20had%20no%20other%20choice.%20Like%20Roylin%2C%20she%20wished%20to%20prevent%20Scottish%20secession%2C%20but%20not%20for%20the%20same%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScotland%2C%20Grace%20explains%2C%20is%20ho