B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222549%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22allison%20janney%20as%20grace%20penn%20in%20the%20diplomat.%20she's%20wearing%20%20burgendy%20suit%20and%20grey%20blouse%20and%20has%20a%20short%20blonde%20bob%2C%20and%20is%20standing%20outside%20a%20home%20with%20her%20hands%20resting%20on%20a%20railing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723f0e2a0a0cc14f2256619%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAllison%20Janney%20as%20Grace%20Penn%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Diplomat.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210a79592-26af-491b-923f-2adcd4e2bbe2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20VP%20job%20is%20open%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20be%20Kate's%20for%20the%20taking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%20for%20us%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Diplomat%26quot%3B%20has%20already%20been%20renewed%20for%20a%20third%20season%20that's%20already%20in%20production%20in%20New%20York.%20Russell%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Ftv-movies%2Ftv-movie-reviews%2Fthe-diplomat-review-netflix-keri-russell-the-americans-tv-political-thriller-feminism-vp-rufus-sewell-1234715683%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERolling%20Stone%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she's%20already%20read%20all%20of%20season%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20good%20in%20the%20way%20I%20want%20things%20to%20be%20good%2C%20and%20I%20just%20can't%20believe%20that%20it's%20still%20getting%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20Grace%20is%20the%20president%2C%20the%20VP%20job%20is%20wide%20open%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20may%20not%20necessarily%20be%20Kate's%20for%20the%20taking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20twenty-fifth%20amendment%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Constitution%3A%20%26quot%3BWhenever%20there%20is%20a%20vacancy%20in%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Vice%20President%2C%20the%20President%20shall%20nominate%20a%20