0of%20money%20keep%20you%20from%20living%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20thinks%20it's%20essential%20to%20examine%20our%20relationships%20with%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20call%20it%20the%20attachment%20to%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%5Bwhen%5D%20you're%20so%20afraid%20to%20live.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20example%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bscarcity%20attachment%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20a%20client%20who%20came%20to%20his%20office%20during%20a%20rainstorm%2C%20and%20she%20was%20soaked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20she%20had%20parked%20in%20the%20underground%20garage%2C%20so%20he%20asked%20her%20how%20she%20got%20so%20wet.%20She%20told%20him%20her%20car%20had%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20roof%2C%20and%20she%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20fix%20it.%20But%20Taylor%20knew%20that%20the%20client%20had%20earned%20%2450%2C000%20in%20interest%20on%20her%20investments%20in%20the%20last%20month%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20falls%20firmly%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Babundance%20attachment%26quot%3B%20camp.%20If%20he%20lost%20everything%20today%2C%20Taylor%20is%20confident%20he%20could%20earn%20it%20back%20in%2012%20months%20because%20he%20understands%20the%20principles%20of%20money%20and%20he's%20not%20afraid%20of%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he's%20also%20not%20afraid%20to%20branch%20out%3A%20He%20owns%20eight%20businesses%2C%20and%20his%20latest%20is%20not%20in%20financial%20services%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.socreamalicious.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECreamalicious%3C%2Fa%3E%20ice%20cream%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Taylor's%20famous%20clients%20need%20to%20take%20a%20more%20cautious%20approach%20to%20money%20management.%20%26quot%3BThe%20athlete%2C%20the%20entertainer%2C%20has%20to%20be%20more%20disciplined%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20only%20way%20I%20know%20how%20to%20make%20money%20is%20by%20th