20directly%20benefits%20thousands%20of%20residents%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139499%2Fdevanahalli-toilets-karnataka-odf-fstp-swachh-bharat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDevanahalli%20%3C%2Fa%3Emunicipality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20this%20work%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20treated%20wastewater%20from%20a%20sewage%20treatment%20plant%20is%20first%20pumped%20into%20Bagalur%20Lake%2C%20where%20it%20is%20diluted%20with%20rainwater.%20This%20water%20is%20then%20directed%20to%20Devanahalli%E2%80%99s%20Sihineeru%20Kere%20Lake%20through%20a%20pipeline%2C%20further%20diluted%20with%20rainwater%2C%20and%20subsequently%20filtered%20through%20the%20earth%20to%20recharge%20the%20aquifer.%20The%20water%20is%20then%20picked%20up%20from%20the%20aquifer%20through%20a%20dug%20well%20and%20shallow%20filter%20borewells%2C%20treated%2C%20and%20then%20supplied%20to%20the%20town%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20this%20an%20indirect%20potable%20water%20reuse%20project%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20project%20uses%20an%20environmental%20buffer%20like%20a%20lake%20for%20dilution%20with%20rainwater%20and%2For%20a%20groundwater%20aquifer%20for%20earth%20filtration.%20This%20water%20eventually%20goes%20through%20a%20final%20treatment%20stage%20before%20it%20is%20supplied%20to%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20project%20