2C%20and%20I%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20policy%20gaps%20in%20this%20sector.%20It%20was%20an%20issue%20close%20to%20my%20heart.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20background%20as%20a%20teacher%20and%20facilitator%20equipped%20her%20with%20the%20skills%20to%20help%20build%20the%20organisation%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20about%20thinking%20and%20theorising%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20doing%20in%20practice.%20You%20have%20to%20find%20the%20right%20words%2C%20create%20a%20structure%2C%20and%20develop%20a%20framework%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20CEO%2C%20Ramya%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20both%20the%20sector%20and%20the%20CCIs%20from%20which%20these%20youths%20transition.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20constantly%20working%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20what%E2%80%99s%20available%20and%20what%E2%80%99s%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20about%20much%20more%20than%20just%20providing%20shelter%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20creating%20opportunities%20for%20growth%2C%20healing%2C%20and%20independence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnity%20through%20diversity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouth%20find%20their%20way%20to%20WeLive%20through%20a%20dynamic%20outreach%20programme%2C%20explains%20Prithvi%20Shukla%2C%20programme%20manager%20at%20the%20NGO.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20established%20a%20national%20care%20leavers%20association%20and%20work%20closely%20with%20district%20child%20protection%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20partner%20with%20agencies%20and%20visit%20various%20CCIs%2C%20where%20we%20introduce%20our%20p